Saikei Shin is regarded as the essence of {{ill|Mercury|ja|水星|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (辰星) and governs punishment and judicial matters. It is considered inauspicious to initiate enterprises, relocate, or engage in activities directed toward the direction of Saikei Shin's residence. However, as this deity is associated with military force and weapons, it is considered auspicious to manufacture or purchase weapons, blades, or engage in lawsuits and disputes. If the actions in legal or contentious matters are justifiable, the influence of Saikei Shin is deemed favorable; otherwise, one is likely to face punishment.
Saikei Shin also has attributes associated with {{ill|Earth (Wu Xing)|ja|土|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. Activities such as earth-moving, sowing seeds, or planting trees in the direction of Saikei Shin's presence are considered ill-advised and inauspicious.
== Saikei Shin's Position == Saikei Shin's position varies based on the year's {{ill|Chinese zodiac|ja|十二支|qq=draft|qq=draft}}: * Rat (子) → Rabbit (卯) * Ox (丑) → Dog (戌) * Tiger (寅) → Snake (巳) * Rabbit (卯) → Rat (子) * Dragon (辰) → Dragon (辰) * Snake (巳) → Monkey (申) * Horse (午) → Horse (午) * Goat (未) → Ox (丑) * Monkey (申) → Tiger (寅) * Rooster (酉) → Rooster (酉) * Dog (戌) → Goat (未) * Pig (亥) → Pig (亥) == See Also == * {{ill|Eight Guardian Deities|ja|八将神|1=Eight Directional Deities|qq=draft|qq=draft}} * {{ill|Guardian Deity of Directions|ja|方位神|1=Directional deity|1=Directional deity|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
